t","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":"wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N","boundElements":[],"x":1980,"angle":0,"y":-340,"width":280},{"seed":2119655877,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xVhR7AxrC5Wu4IsR5KmiL","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":true,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1782160491311,"locked":false,"text":"Принцип:\nработает зеркально относительно\nnMOS: низкий сигнал на затворе\nоткрывает канал, высокий сигнал\nзакрывает канал.","version":328,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzZ8","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Принцип:\nработает зеркально относительно nMOS: низкий сигнал на затворе открывает канал, высокий сигнал закрывает канал.","height":100,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":["b6vWIwKSK59TpRo_wkPZI"],"versionNonce":670877905,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":"wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N","boundElements":[],"x":1980,"angle":0,"y":-260,"width":280},{"seed":2092758789,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"lEEsHTTbgnXykJC9dbHG3","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":true,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1782160491311,"locked":false,"text":"Логика:\nзатвор = 0 -> открыт;\nзатвор = 1 -> закрыт.","version":309,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzZG","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Логика:\nзатвор = 0 -> открыт;\nзатвор = 1 -> закрыт.","height":60,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":["b6vWIwKSK59TpRo_wkPZI"],"versionNonce":2041424063,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":"wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N","boundElements":[],"x":1980,"angle":0,"y":-140,"width":280.00000000000006},{"seed":559580427,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"oeM86JNl5jK2K_kNZ94mS","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":true,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1782160491311,"locked":false,"text":"В цифровых схемах pMOS обычно\nиспользуется для соединения\nвыхода с питанием, то есть для\nполучения 1.","version":323,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzZO","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"В цифровых схемах pMOS обычно используется для соединения выхода с питанием, то есть для получения 1.","height":80,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":["b6vWIwKSK59TpRo_wkPZI"],"versionNonce":2146272945,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":"wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N","boundElements":[],"x":1980,"angle":0,"y":-60,"width":279.99999999999989},{"isDeleted":true,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":["wmebY1rlE7zhQZOe6VjFR"],"index":"b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzZV","backgroundColor":"transparent","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":307,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1782160491311,"id":"iCIh91sJlUlLjLqjfzejB","x":1620,"seed":1986895467,"boundElements":[],"y":60,"opacity":100,"height":160,"width":660,"frameId":"wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N","strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1687697631},{"seed":1452916875,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xX891hdv6zTzs1RpTD_mt","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":true,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1782160491311,"locked":false,"text":"Т.е. в зависимости от материала bulk \/ body можно получить 2 различных\nтранзистора:\n- Если материал тела – p-type полупроводник с n+ истоком и n+ стоком, то\nмы получаем nMOS\n- Если материал тела – n-type полупроводник с p+ истоком и p+ стоком, то\nмы получаем pMOS","version":571,"autoResize":false,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzZZ","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Т.е. в зависимости от материала bulk \/ body можно получить 2 различных транзистора:\n- Если материал тела – p-type полупроводник с n+ истоком и n+ стоком, то м